  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large tagine or Dutch oven, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the crumbled goat cheese, cumin, cinnamon, and salt. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the chopped figs and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the tagine to the preheated oven and bake for 20-25 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Garnish with chopped pistachios and serve warm."
